#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1950
msgid "MFA"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1951
msgid "Configure security settings for multi-factor authentication."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1953
msgid ""
"The default recommendation for secure deployment is to host Mattermost "
"within your own private network, with VPN clients on mobile, so "
"everything works under your existing security policies and authentication"
" protocols, which may already include multi-factor authentication."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1955
msgid ""
"If you choose to run Mattermost outside your private network, bypassing "
"your existing security protocols, it is recommended you set up a multi-"
"factor authentication service specifically for accessing Mattermost."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1959
msgid "Enable Multi-factor Authentication"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1961
msgid ""
"**True**: When true, users with LDAP and email authentication will be "
"given the option to require a phone-based passcode, in addition to their "
"password-based authentication, to sign-in to the Mattermost server. "
"Specifically, they will be asked to download the `Google Authenticator "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_Authenticator>`__ app to their iOS "
"or Android mobile device, connect the app with their account, and then "
"enter a passcode generated by the app on their phone whenever they log in"
" to the Mattermost server."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1963
msgid "**False**: Multi-factor authentication is disabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1966
msgid ""
"This feature's ``config.json`` setting is "
"``\"EnableMultifactorAuthentication\": false`` with options ``true`` and "
"``false``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1970
#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2753
msgid "Enforce Multi-factor Authentication"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1973
msgid ""
"**True**: When true, `multi-factor authentication (MFA) "
"<https://docs.mattermost.com/deployment/auth.html>`__ is required for "
"login. New users will be required to configure MFA on sign-up. Logged in "
"users without MFA configured are redirected to the MFA setup page until "
"configuration is complete. If your system has users with login options "
"other than AD/LDAP and email, MFA must be enforced with the "
"authentication provider outside of Mattermost."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1975
msgid "**False**: Multi-factor authentication is optional."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:1978
#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2761
msgid ""
"This feature's ``config.json`` setting is "
"``\"EnforceMultifactorAuthentication\": false`` with options ``true`` and"
" ``false``."
msgstr ""

