" name of users in Mattermost. When set, users cannot edit their first "
"name, since it is synchronized with the LDAP server. When left blank, "
"users can set their first name in Account Settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2157
#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2486
msgid ""
"This feature's ``config.json`` setting is ``\"FirstNameAttribute\": "
"\"\"`` with string input."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2161
#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2490
msgid "Last Name Attribute"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2162
msgid ""
"(Optional) The attribute in the AD/LDAP server used to populate the last "
"name of users in Mattermost. When set, users cannot edit their last name,"
" since it is synchronized with the LDAP server. When left blank, users "
"can set their last name in Account Settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2165
#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2494
msgid ""
"This feature's ``config.json`` setting is ``\"LastNameAttribute\": \"\"``"
" with string input."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2169
#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2498
msgid "Nickname Attribute"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2170
msgid ""
"(Optional) The attribute in the AD/LDAP server used to populate the "
"nickname of users in Mattermost. When set, users cannot edit their "
"nickname, since it is synchronized with the LDAP server. When left blank,"
