"if you are getting timeout errors caused by a slow AD/LDAP server."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2261
msgid ""
"This feature's ``config.json`` setting is ``\"QueryTimeout\": 60`` with "
"numerical input."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2265
msgid "AD/LDAP Test"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2266
msgid ""
"This button can be used to test the connection to the AD/LDAP server. If "
"the test is successful, it shows a confirmation message and if there is a"
" problem with the configuration settings it will show an error message."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2269
msgid "AD/LDAP Synchronize Now"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2270
msgid ""
"This button causes AD/LDAP synchronization to occur as soon as it is "
"pressed. Use it whenever you have made a change in the AD/LDAP server you"
" want to take effect immediately. After using the button, the next "
"AD/LDAP synchronization will occur after the time specified by the "
"Synchronization Interval."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2272
msgid ""
"You can monitor the status of the synchronization job in the table below "
"this button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2275
msgid ""
"If synchronization **Status** displays as ``Pending`` and does not "
"complete, make sure that the **Enable Synchronization with AD/LDAP** "
"setting is set to ``true``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2282
msgid "SAML"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2286
#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2676
msgid ""
"In line with Microsoft ADFS guidance we recommend `configuring intranet "
