#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2917
msgid ""
"**False**: The Integrations > Outgoing Webhooks section of Account "
"Settings is hidden and all outgoing webhooks are disabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/config-settings.rst:2922
msgid ""
"This feature's ``config.json`` setting is ``\"EnableOutgoingWebhooks\": "
"true`` with options ``true`` and ``false``."
